title: Couple With Heart Woman Person Medium Light Skin Tone No Skin Tone
description: Illustrates a couple, a person and a man, sharing a kiss with a heart symbol, representing love and romance. The person has a medium-light skin tone, while the man has a default, unspecified skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: This heartfelt emoji on Apple devices features a couple, a woman with a medium-light skin tone and a person with a default skin tone, united by a glowing red heart. Apple’s distinctive glossy 3D shading and realistic lighting give the figures a warm, approachable feel with softly rounded edges. The heart radiates with a vibrant, polished sheen, perfectly capturing the essence of love and connection. On Apple devices, this emoji is a tender representation of partnership and affection, ideal for expressing shared joy and deep emotional bonds.
